## Future Work

- **Automatic bat detection** using a pre-trained object detector (YOLOv8 or similar) to replace manual ROI
- **Deep learning classifier** trained on labeled contact/no-contact frame patches
- **Audio snick detection** using spectral analysis of the bat-ball impact sound
- **Real-time processing** with GPU acceleration for live match use
- **Multi-camera fusion** to improve detection confidence

